**path:**
cd ~/Desktop/
ls # lists all the files in this path
cd .. # 返回上一级
gwd # 当前位置/上次停留的位置

**open file:**
open -a "Application" filename

**move:**
mv filename path

**create new folders:**
cd path mkdir "foldername"

**delete files/folders:**
rm -i filename
rm -iR foldername

**copy files:**
cp -v path-old/filename path-new # rename while copying/moving possible

**download files from the internet:**
curl -O [URL of file you want to download]

**run python:**
python filename
